Web Server

#Attacking_machine

  1. Add the domain services.local to the etc/hosts file.
<MACHINE IP>     services.local

  1. Visit http://services.local/contact.html.


    You can see the email format.

  2. Visit http://services.local/about.html.

    These are some names you can use later.

  3. Create a file called users.txt with one row for every user. In this file create a row with every team's member with the format you saw on the previous step.

    • j.doe for Joanne Doe
    • j.rock for Jack Rock
    • w.masters for Will Masters
    • j.larusso for Johnny LaRusso

Next step: Kerbrute
